column2: SELECT   p.objID, p.ra, p.dec,   p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,  p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z  FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID  JOIN Photoz e ON e.objID = p.objID ORDER by x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
